# Reusable Terraform modules. Populated in Phases 2-5.
#
#   vpc/       Phase 2 — VPC, subnets, NAT, route tables
#   ecr/       Phase 2 — One ECR repo per service with lifecycle policies
#   rds/      Phase 3 — Postgres in private subnets + Secrets Manager
#   eks/      Phase 4 — EKS cluster + managed node groups (using LabRole)
#   platform/ Phase 5 — helm_release resources for cert-manager,
#                       ingress-nginx, kube-prometheus-stack, loki-stack
